# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [Unreleased]

### Added
- Initial release of the Text Anonymizer library
- Core functionality for text anonymization and de-anonymization
- Entity recognition for PERSON, ORGANIZATION, LOCATION, EMAIL, and URL
- Basic test suite
- README with usage instructions and API reference

### Changed
- Improved project structure for better maintainability

### Fixed
- Issue with entity numbering in anonymization process
